{"data":[{"date":"07:38 22/08","title":"Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Juventus ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/ronaldo-khong-the-giup-juventus-tiep-tuc-thong-tri-nuoc-y.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Allan c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i Napoli c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Serie A.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau khi chia tay Real Madrid v\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus g\u1eb7p Chievo Verona \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 2018/19.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hay ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Juventus c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Se h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Se h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/ronaldo-khong-the-giup-juventus-tiep-tuc-thong-tri-nuoc-y.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Allan c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i Napoli c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CR7 v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Italia. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil: &ldquo;S\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng cao.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng r\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng Ronaldo c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. Juventus ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Serie A th\u00eam n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2u.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t s\u00edt sao v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i cho th\u1ea5y Napoli ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 Juventus trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Ronaldo s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 khi Juventus ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Lazio, b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh Napoli trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5755","checkdouble":"195019"},{"date":"08:26 22/08","title":"H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/hang-loat-doi-bong-lon-nhan-don-dau-vu-pjanic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus t\u1eeb Roma v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hang-loat-doi-bong-lon-nhan-don-dau-vu-pjanic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n mua Pjanic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Pjanic ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn 44 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Pjanic l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A v\u00e0 C\u00fap QG Italia v\u1edbi Juventus trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-tinh-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-pjanic-180-194470.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Miralem Pjanic</span>, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City c\u0169ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990. Khi m\u00e0 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec Los Blancos \u0111ang m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a trong vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pjanic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN nh\u1eafm Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus vs Porto Pjanic\" title=\"Juventus vs Porto Pjanic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/23/juventus-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-man-city-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Juventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i, anh s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pjanic h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Juventus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Miralem Pjanic l\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd y\u00ean t\u00e2m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5754","checkdouble":"195028"},{"date":"08:57 22/08","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169, Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u201ctr\u00ean tr\u1eddi\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/22/real-phai-tra-120-trieu-euro-de-mua-rodrigo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rodrigo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Rodrigo Moreno. Anh ghi t\u1edbi 19 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, bao g\u1ed3m 16 t\u1ea1i La Liga, gi\u00fap Valencia gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQua \u0111\u00f3, Rodrigo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/real-phai-tra-120-trieu-euro-de-mua-rodrigo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Rodrigo t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Real m\u00f9a 2009/2010. Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 g\u00ec HLV Julen Lopetegui khi t\u1eebng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c tr\u00ean U21 v\u00e0 \u0110TQG T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u1ea3i mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Mateu Alemany c\u1ee7a Valencia \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng Real ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Rodrigo. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00fang \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Real Madrid\u201d, Alemany n\u00f3i v\u1edbi BeIN SPORT khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u201cN\u1ebfu h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng Rodrigo c\u00f3 v\u1ebb r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a La Liga m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19, Valencia \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a Atletico Madrid 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh Rodrigo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d sau b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Angel Correa ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-voi-80-trieu-euro-cho-rodrigo-moi-di-cho-khac-180-192338.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/goc-real-voi-80-trieu-euro-cho-rodrigo-moi-di-cho-khac.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-voi-80-trieu-euro-cho-rodrigo-moi-di-cho-khac-180-192338.html\">G\u00f3c Real: V\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Rodrigo? M\u1eddi \u0111i ch\u1ed7 kh\u00e1c!</span><br>\r\n<span>Bi\u1ebft Real Madrid \u0111ang kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t m\u0169i c\u00f4ng thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, Valencia \u00e9p gi\u00e1 tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Rodrigo. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-san-sang-nha-nguoi-thua-rafinha-180-194985.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d Rafinha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-180-194897.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang-180-194880.html\">Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-194831.html\">Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-hazard-172-194702.html\">HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5753","checkdouble":"195036"},{"date":"08:04 22/08","title":"Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 thay th\u1ebf Mourinho \u1edf Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/zidane-duoc-ung-ho-thay-the-mourinho-o-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf Lee Sharpe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2018 v\u00e0 Zinedine Zidane l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia tay Real Madrid tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh vinh quang h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Zinedine Zidane c\u0169ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf Juventus, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man Utd m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Zidane thay Mourinho l\u00e0m HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Zidane thay Mourinho l\u00e0m HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/zidane-duoc-ung-ho-thay-the-mourinho-o-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zidane thay Mourinho l\u00e0m HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng HLV c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u0111ang lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i \u1edf Old Trafford b\u1edfi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Brighton 3-2 MU, c\u1ef1u Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf Lee Sharpe m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i ngay trong n\u0103m nay v\u00e0 c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Zidane cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 47 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;Mourinho l\u1ea1i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0nh m\u00f3ng ng\u1ef1a r\u1ed3i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac hay bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Man Utd. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 nghe n\u00f3i \u00f4ng \u1ea5y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0a ra ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec \u0111\u00e1.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Mourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u1edd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111ang ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n quan t\u00e2m g\u00ec n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ebfn CLB n\u00e0y. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta b\u1edfi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ra \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng Sinh n\u0103m nay.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Zidane, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man Utd \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i \u1edf c\u1ea3 c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 HLV, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat ng\u00f4i sao, ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\">Man Utd thua th\u1ea3m: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Jose Mourinho gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai Man City nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Pep Guardiola ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/Du-am-Brighton-vs-MU-Dung-roi-Jose,-tien-khong-the-mua-dang-cap-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\">M.U phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Jose Mourinho: Con thuy\u1ec1n m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng</span><br>\r\nN\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton. L\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5752","checkdouble":"195020"},{"date":"08:30 22/08","title":"B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi danh t\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/bat-ngo-voi-danh-tinh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-mua-giai-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville v\u00e0 Jamie Carragher s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n Premier League 2018/19, bao g\u1ed3m danh t\u00ednh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, top 4, vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u1eb1m \u1edf s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi gi\u1ed1ng nhau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0nh, c\u1ea3 hai c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn David Silva. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng Mohamed Salah, Harry Kane hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Big Six, \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Manchester City.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville v\u00e0 Jamie Carragher d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville v\u00e0 Jamie Carragher d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/bat-ngo-voi-danh-tinh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-mua-giai-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville v\u00e0 Jamie Carragher d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Neville v\u00e0 Carragher c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u1ea5y l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man City khi c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Liverpool. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19 sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p th\u00fa v\u1ecb gi\u1eefa hai huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f2n \u1edf c\u1ea3 danh s\u00e1ch th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh top 4, bao g\u1ed3m Liverpool v\u00e0 Manchester United c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Tottenham, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t su\u00f4t t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal thay t\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn khi s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1eadt b\u00e3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 Champions League. Neville v\u00e0 Carragher c\u0169ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Everton s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 chen ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m 6 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t (Neville &ndash; Alisson Becker v\u00e0 Carragher &ndash; Naby Keita) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t (Phil Foden c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 Ryan Sessegnon c\u1ee7a Fulham).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t, Neville v\u00e0 Carragher chia r\u1ebd quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Mohamed Salah m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 Harry Kane.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5751","checkdouble":"195025"},{"date":"08:36 22/08","title":"Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua sao Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/4/man-city-phu-nhan-mua-cillessen-vao-thang-1.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Jasper Cillessen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Man City nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au khi Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi 6 th\u00e1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mua Jasper Cillessen v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mua Jasper Cillessen v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Man-City-mua-Jasper-Cillessen-vao-thang-1-nam-2019-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City nh\u1eafm Cillessen thay Bravo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Ederson, song h\u1ecd c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7. Theo Daily Mail, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJasper Cillessen l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man City. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Camp Nou, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCillessen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia quan t\u00e2m, song anh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu Man City t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Cillessen</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jasper Cillessen\" title=\"Jasper Cillessen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/HLV-Valverde-muon-Cillessen-o-lai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Jasper Cillessen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua th\u00eam th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Man City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m Jasper Cillessen, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man xanh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-muon-cillessen-o-lai-barca-180-193784.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</span>. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 Marc-Andre ter Stegen.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Valverde mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u01b0ng \u00fd, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5750","checkdouble":"195029"},{"date":"19:55 21/08","title":"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/bi-gioi-chuyen-mon-chi-trich-sau-tran-gap-nhat-ban-hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ec1u 21/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft khi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, trong khi Quang H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3n b\u00e1c nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;&ldquo;Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch v\u00e0 ph\u00ea ph\u00e1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Olympic Nepal, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng sau. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00ec ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. T\u1ed1n s\u1ee9c th\u00ec tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o c\u0169ng t\u1ed1n s\u1ee9c th\u00f4i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c r\u1ed3i, khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 phi\u1ec1n l\u00f2ng&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Theo \u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1nsong kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu, \u00f4ng Park t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i kh\u00e9o: &ldquo;T\u00f4i xin gi\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u Bahrain \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-184-195009.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-184-195009.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 21/8: H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Mourinho b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t gi\u1ed1ng Wenger,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd Chosun (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD?</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u1eeba qua, trong khi L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 suy...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5749","checkdouble":"195010"},{"date":"20:10 21/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-lap-ky-luc-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD d\u00f9 chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</h2><h2>B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o sau 3 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-lap-ky-luc-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh g\u1ed1c Ng\u1ecdc L\u1eb7c (Thanh H\u00f3a) c\u00f9ng \u0110T U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2017, ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi hai l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iraq v\u00e0 Qatar.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n anh V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng). Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Park Hang Seo quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i U23 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00ec th\u1ebf ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0 n\u00ean Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong khung g\u1ed7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng &quot;v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh&quot; su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-184-195009.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 21/8: H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam-168-194974.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/lo-dien-don-vi-nam-ban-quyen-phat-song-asiad-2018-tai-viet-nam-292-194963.html\">N\u00f3ng: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5748","checkdouble":"195011"},{"date":"20:26 21/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/14/nong-nam-dinh-san-sang-bo-vleague-vi-ly-do-bat-ngo.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ec9nh, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League \u0111\u1ec3 quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t.</h2><h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean OnSports, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ee9c x\u00fac r\u1eb1ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ec9nh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC: &quot;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/nong-nam-dinh-san-sang-bo-vleague-vi-ly-do-bat-ngo.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 ki\u1ec3u mu\u1ed1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu th\u1ea3 h\u1eb3n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec c\u1ee9 n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nu\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau b\u1ea3y n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i V-League \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 20 v\u00f2ng, \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1p ch\u00f3t khi ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u n\u00ean n\u1ed7i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a quen v\u1edbi nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu kinh ph\u00ed ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng nh\u1edd b\u1ea7u s\u1eefa c\u1ee7a t\u1ec9nh n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf V-League. N\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng 21 V-League 2018, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC t\u1ea1i V-League 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-191331.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng ngay t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-nam-dinh-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-sau-vu-nao-loan-tren-san-thien-truong-168-190948.html\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t sau v\u1ee5 n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cdv-nam-dinh-dai-nao-san-thien-truong-nguoi-trong-cuoc-noi-gi-168-190610.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5747","checkdouble":"195012"},{"date":"19:47 21/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 21/8: H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Mourinho b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t gi\u1ed1ng Wenger,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb HLV Arsene Wenger, Thierry Henry \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bourdeaux. Henry t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong vai tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 218 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 218 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/duc-chinh-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gabriel Jesus t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Sergio Aguero tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n cho Man City t\u1ea1i Premier League.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Farabi Firdausy c\u1ee7a Indonesia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c \u0110\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u1ec7m l\u00f2ng hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Firmino \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Philippe Coutinho. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Firmino \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 36 b\u00e0n, k\u00e9m Coutinho 5 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Chelsea \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Eden Hazard nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ve v\u00e3n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Hazard s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 300.000 b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1eadm n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-7, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 to ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p. D\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho\" title=\"Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Man Utd.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Arsenal, Ian Wright nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Jose Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 chung ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh v\u1edbi Arsene Wenger trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i, khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea5t l\u00f2ng tin nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb Transfermarkt, Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao g\u1ea5p 16 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam (2.03 tri\u1ec7u so v\u1edbi 125.000 euro). D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i trong khi Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vincent Kompany kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Man City kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2017-18. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 10 n\u0103m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn ng\u00e0y 21/8:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-pogba-chi-trich-huyen-thoai-mu-172-195008.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-sap-mua-duoc-gavin-bazunu-172-195006.html\">Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tu\u1ed5i teen</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/marc-cucurella-muon-roi-barca-180-195005.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Barca quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2108-180-195004.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/08</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-palace-02-liverpool-172-195001.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5746","checkdouble":"195009"},{"date":"06:05 22/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/8: Zidane thay Mourinho v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-228-zidane-thay-mourinho-va-tieng-noi-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 22/8.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Zidane thay Mourinho</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 228 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 228 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-vi-man-utd-zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Zinedine Zidane</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang ta l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111i b\u00e0n lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Zidane khi ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eeba vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eady?\u201d \u2013 M\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ea5p cao \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp. Jose Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 cao b\u1ecb Man Utd sa th\u1ea3i b\u1edfi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf c\u00f9ng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn kh\u00f3 h\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, \u00edt l\u00e2u sau khi chia tay Real Madrid tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh vinh quang.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ecnh ti\u1ebft m\u1edbi trong chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Man Utd<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 228 Zidane thay Mourinho v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 228 Zidane thay Mourinho v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-228-Zidane-thay-Mourinho-va-tieng-noi-cua-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Anthony Martial</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anthony Martial v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng Jose Mourinho v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng gi\u00fap \u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd, Martial th\u1ef1c ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trong khi ch\u00ednh Mourinho m\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf b\u00e1n qu\u00e1ch \u0111i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 23 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona v\u1eabn c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i Yerry Mina nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina chinh thuc toi Everton\" title=\"Mina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Everton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/yerry-mina-chinh-thuc-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Yerry Mina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Barcelona v\u1eabn g\u00e0i th\u00eam v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i (54 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u2013 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro), tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2020. Mina l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Goodison Park trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Andre Gomes theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City c\u1ea7u vi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Bravo\" title=\"thu mon Bravo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Claudio-Bravo-dinh-chan-thuong-nang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Claudio Bravo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 nguy c\u01a1 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Claudio Bravo c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Joe Hart \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Burnley, khung g\u1ed7 s\u00e2n Etihad hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Ederson Moraes. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i Aro Muric ng\u01b0\u1eddi Montenegro l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 Lan NAC Breda.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfp theo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Drinkwater\" title=\"Drinkwater\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/26/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-Vi-Man-Utd,-Zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-Juventus-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Drinkwater</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 l\u00e0 Jorginho, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9o theo, t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p thanh l\u00fd trong th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. Sau khi Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan, Danny Drinkwater c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo ph\u1ea3i chia tay Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao Tottenham chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Paris Saint-Germain<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Rose cua Tottenham\" title=\"Danny Rose cua Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/Mourinho-len-tieng-vu-MU-mua-Danny-Rose-cua-Tottenham--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Rose</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u1edf Anh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u00e1c CLB Premier League kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Danny Rose v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Spurs. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p PSG theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5745","checkdouble":"195016"},{"date":"18:25 21/08","title":"T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Barca quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/marc-cucurella-muon-roi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marc Cucurella mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i 20 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Blaugrana.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Cucurella kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarc Cucurella gia nh\u1eadp l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o La Masia c\u1ee7a Barcelona t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Espanyol n\u0103m 2-2012. Nh\u01b0ng 6 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 20 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Barca \u1edf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Murcia t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 2017.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Barca B, Cucurella thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ecdi l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eeb U16 t\u1edbi U20. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb sinh n\u0103m 1998 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t m\u00e3n khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ernesto Valverde s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marc Cucurella mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marc Cucurella mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/marc-cucurella-muon-roi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marc Cucurella mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo, Marc Cucurella mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh t\u1eebng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 CLB c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 Mainz v\u00e0 Borussia Monchengladbach quan t\u00e2m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Cucurella quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng tr\u00f4i qua, Cucurella kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng Jordi Alba v\u00e0 Lucas Digne m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i Barca. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi Digne \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Everton, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u1eabn t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c Filipe Luis (Atletico Madrid) ho\u1eb7c Juan Bernat (Bayern Munich) thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng Cucurella.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 20, Cucurella kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1ecf nhoi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh Barca. Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Cucurella ra s\u00e2n 37 l\u1ea7n cho Barca B, ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 4 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-gia-mua-adrien-rabiot-180-194994.html\">Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua sao tr\u1ebb Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-gia-ban-rakitic-cho-psg-180-194989.html\">Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Rakitic cho PSG?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-san-sang-nha-nguoi-thua-rafinha-180-194985.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d Rafinha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/dortmund-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-paco-alcacer-180-194972.html\">Dortmund l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-194914.html\">Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5744","checkdouble":"195005"},{"date":"00:17 22/08","title":"Real Madrid l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed ph\u0169 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/real-madrid-cho-muon-martin-odergaard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy, Martin Odegaard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan v\u1edbi th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Real Madrid cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Martin Odegaard<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martin Odegaard, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Real Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n hai l\u1ea7n. Odegaard hai m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y sang Heerenveen theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Martin Odegaard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Martin Odegaard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/real-madrid-cho-muon-martin-odergaard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Real Madrid cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Martin Odergaard th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong hai m\u00f9a kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Heerenveen, Odegaard ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n sau 43 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Julen Lopetegui gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Odegaard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Vitesse theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vitesse l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Odegaard v\u1edbi Vitesse s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 30/6/2019.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Odegaard n\u00f3i g\u00ec?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 12 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Na Uy nh\u01b0ng Odegaard v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, Odegaard cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Vitesse. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Vitesse trao cho\".<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Martin Odegaard:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid-180-194418.html\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/than-dong-khong-lon-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-real-madrid-180-161707.html\">\u201cTh\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u201d v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-trong-thang-mot-172-151840.html\">Real ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/sao-tre-than-dong-real-martin-odegaard-re-bong-hay-dut-diem-toi-328-146942.html\">Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Real r\u00ea b\u00f3ng t\u1ef1a Messi, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Bendtner</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rashford-khien-than-dong-real-madrid-phuc-sat-dat-172-142414.html\">Rashford khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Real Madrid ph\u1ee5c s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nghi-van-zidane-lai-bi-ep-dung-odegaard-o-champions-league-180-142147.html\">Nghi v\u1ea5n: Zidane l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb \u201c\u00e9p\u201d d\u00f9ng Odegaard \u1edf Champions League?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5743","checkdouble":"195015"}]}